dct_description_sm: Map of Western Australia showing government railways, railway construction, telegraph lines, stations and stock routes.
Includes inset map of Australia showing major railways.
"John T. Short Commissioner of Railways, E.E. Light Chief Engineer of Existing Lines"--Government logotype.
